ecahedron</a> <a href=3D"https://mathworld.wolfram.com/GreatIcosahedron.htm=
l">great
 icosahedron</a>, 11th <a href=3D"https://mathworld.wolfram.com/Icosahedron=
Stellations.html">icosahedron stellation</a>,
 and <a href=3D"https://mathworld.wolfram.com/SmallStellatedDodecahedron.ht=
ml">small stellated dodecahedron</a>.
</p>
